         <abstract id="aspace_04ccfe2b296d44f61e3921013498121f">The papers concern Smith's work on the Arden Shakespeare Series and include notes and collations for several plays, documents relating to editorial techniques and a small amount of professional correspondence.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n50013401" source="naf">
               <part>Smith, David Nichol, 1875-1962</part>
            </persname>
